Name: {FILTER}
Description: Filters a player variable by a certain type.
Stores Players: YES
Usage: {FILTER:NAME:TYPE:INPUT}
Variable Type: Numerical

Arguments:

<name>
  Required: YES
  Type: Player Variable
  The name of the variable to filter.

<type>
  Required: YES
  Type: String (Message/Text)
  The mode to use to filter.

<input>
  Required: YES
  Type: Any Type
  What to use as the filter (RoleType, ZoneType, etc)

The following options are valid mode options:
- USERID
- PLAYERID
- ROLE
- TEAM
- ROOM
- ZONE
- INV
- HELDITEM
- GROUP
- ISSTAFF
Invalid options will result in a script error.
